    participants without confirm status and alarm times the server
    uses the information taken from the database instead of throwing
    an permission error.

* 2006-12-21 - martin.kauss@open-xchange.com
 
  - Fixed bugs 4557 and bug 4119. Appointments in a shared folder are
    now changeable even if the user is a participant. Additional, a
    wrong statement regarding resource handling has been fixed. Update
    an appoinment and adding resources works now.

  - Fixed bugs 4377 and 4497. Whole day recurring appointments now gets
    calculated correct. Additional a user who deletes an appointment
    from his personal folder gets removed from the participant list
    correctly. The appointment still exists with at least the creator
    as participant.

